      • getMaxContributors

        int getMaxContributors()
        Returns the maximum number of unique users that can have licenses assigned on this server. A single user that has multiple CALs assigned, only counts as one user towards the server limit.

        the maximum number of unique users that can have licenses assigned on this server.
